ğŸ“Œ Overview

This Terraform project provisions an Ubuntu-based EC2 web server on AWS and configures it using Terraform provisioners.
The project now includes an Amazon S3 remote backend to store Terraform state centrally, enabling safe collaboration and state consistency.

